<p>Inline math <span class="math inline">\(a^2 + b^2 = c^2\)</span>
appears mid-sentence.</p>
<p>Dollar-delimited math <span class="math inline">\(E = mc^2\)</span>
also renders inline.</p>
<p>Display math is set apart:</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\int_0^1 x^2 \, dx = \frac{1}{3}
\]</span></p>
